EN: This nostalgic magazine reminds me of the joyous moments from my childhood.

ZH: 13. 怀旧的风格在时尚界再次流行起来，追求复古的衣物受到年轻人的喜爱。
EN: The nostalgic style is becoming popular in the fashion industry again, and retro clothing is loved by young people.

ZH: 14. 我们计划举办一次怀旧的舞会，让大家重温过去的欢乐时光。
EN: We plan to organize a nostalgic dance party, allowing everyone to relive the joyful moments of the past.

